{
  "title": "Delicate Light Chinese Tofu Noodles",
  "description": "A kid-friendly Chinese dish featuring ginger paste and fermented tofu, this recipe is macrobiotic-friendly and perfect for a light meal. It combines the delicate flavors of ginger and tofu with the simplicity of noodles.",
  "cuisine": "Chinese",
  "diet": [
